- `premiumFor`: 29 → 22, McCabe 2 → 1 (improvement)
- BUT adds new `followUpDiscountFor` function: ~9 mass, McCabe 2
- Net file delta: +2 mass, +1 McCabe (regression)

Neither alternative reduces metrics now, so I stuck with the single `processScenario` refactor.

